  2,36,Sey…óaane hoomti …ìe haa yaltini …ìe e mo∆¥∆¥ere nde …ìe ngonndoo Min mbii …ìe njippo-…óee ngonon a√±ondir…ìe ke…ìon √±ii…ìal dow lesdi ndi e dakmitaare haa happu yonta
